         Daylight.1996.READNFO.2160P.UHD.BLURAY.H265-UNDERTAKERS


         Disaster in a New York tunnel as explosions
         collapse both ends of it. One hero tries to
         help the people inside find their way to safety.

         6.0/10 from 80.402 users
         https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0116040/


         AUDiO.......: ENGLiSH    [TRUEHD + ATMOS // 7.1 // 3.137 kbps]
                       ENGLiSH    [AC3 // 5.1 // 448 kbps]
                       ENGLiSH    [AC3 // 2.0 // 192 kbps]

         ViDEO.......: UNTOUCHED   [23.976FPS // HEVC // 87.254 kbps]

         SUBS........: GERMAN, ENGLISH

         NOTES.......: Some words on this one. MALUS/B0MBARDiERS released this
                       one a while back. What they could not know at this time
                       was that the label (Kino Lorber) revoke their Daylight
                       release. It is not clearly known why Kino Lorber did that
.
                       Still you can not buy the Kino version to this day.
                       Rumors say, that Rob Cohen was not okay with the transfer

                       they did. So now, Turbine Medien has brought us the first

                       worldwide official version of this Stallone "classic".
                       The transfer looks better than the Kino Lorber version
                       (have a look at the compare pics) and is official approve
d
                       by Rob Cohen. Why no REMASTERED tag? Well because there i
s
                       no other official release from it and MALUS/B0MBARDiERS
                       could not know, that they never ever should have gotten
                       this disc. If you want some more infos about that, see
                       the link: https://youtu.be/fCw3dOcxQEg?t=1082


